description	"Rebel Grenadier

^2Weaponry:
- E-11 Blaster Rifle (3)
- MiniMag PTL Launcher [PLX-1] (1 Rocket)
- 2 Dual-Phase Explosive Utility Grenades
-- Based on Frag Grenade
-- Secondary Fire Releases Heavy Smoke
- 1 Pulse Grenade

^8Attributes:
- Stamina (1)
- Reinforcements (1)
- Assemble (1)

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^3[CS1]
- Grapple Hook (2) ^3[CS2 Melee]
- Quick Throw (1) ^3[CS3]

Rebel soldiers specializing in the use of heavy explosives. Contending with a disparity in heavy arms, rebel grenadiers would often use guerilla tactics against Imperial walkers and tanks to great effect."